  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial examines the impact of patients' knowledge of an experienced distant healer's
      efforts to heal them on measures of wound healing, psychosocial functioning, and
      physiological symptoms after plastic surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
